### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer_email": "alice@example.com",
    "amount_cents": 14999,
    "currency": "usd"
}

### Get an order by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### Create payment via stripe-integration for an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/pay

### Create another order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer_email": "bob@example.com",
    "amount_cents": 3950
}

### Cancel an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/2/cancel

### Invalid create (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer_email": "",
    "amount_cents": 0
}

### Get non-existent order (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/99999
